              | #{ __("I'm a 21 years old Information Systems Engineer student from Santa Fe, Argentina. I find myself constantly learning about the latest trends and best practices in both, software development and design. In fact, I believe it is impossible to talk about our profession without highlighting the importance of good design throughout every portion of software that we craft.") }
